Malikia walked into his apartment, put his keys down and headed towards his room.  When he got there he noticed his door open and the light was on.  "What the hell" he said outloud without thinking.  He walked in something was off missing in fact, he couldn't figure out what it was.  He thought that maybe one of his roomates Lucas or Gabe maybe came in to borrow some deoderant or hairgel.  Nope that wasn't it both of those right where he left them, on the shelf above his mirror.  He looked around trying to figure out what was out of place, then he saw it the lock box with the months rent was broken open and emptyed out.  "Fuck" Malikia shouted, he ran to the spot where the emergancy cash was hidden, it was gone too.  He was baffled, "Where could the money have gone" he thought outloud again.  Nothing else was disturbed in the apartment.  He knew it had to either been  Gabe or Lucas, but why?
